      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have got to see this absolute gem! It is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I have taken such good care of it, and it has been kept spotless inside and out. If you are looking for a ride that is basically brand new without the new-car sticker shock, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin, you are going to love it! \u2728",
