    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of naturally aspirated precision, powered by the S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual VANOS. All critical preventative maintenance has been executed, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission offers tight, tactile throws, directing power to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is dialed in with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is fully exploited. Finished in its original factory coating with a pristine interior, this vehicle remains free of mechanical or aesthetic compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
