      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a premium multi-stage ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the hand-stitched leather upholstery is supple and completely free of creasing or bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records documented at the dealership. There are no door dings, no curb rash on the wheels, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a showroom-quality vehicle with a smoke-free, accident-free history.",
      "price": 48500.0,
